	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you read my posting, you will notice that I say do NOT taunt if grouped with a Warrior or Paladin. This is because Rangers are "natural" taunts and they do not have the AC or HP to back this up. If a Ranger is grouped with a Warrior or Paladin and the Ranger also is Taunting, the other tank will probably never get the mob off the Ranger.<br><br>Naturally, if the only tank is a Ranger then Taunting is mandatory.<br><br>As for the tank you mentioned not having the Taunt hot-keyed, that guy is a complete and utter moron. Hopefully you NEVER group with him.<br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
